<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天幫忙聖誕老人<delay8 />
將禮物送來給我。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那禮物是很有趣的玩具家具喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這讓我想起了小時候的事情，<delay8 />
感覺很懷念呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">聖誕老人昨天送的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如同我的期待，<delay8 />是很棒的玩具家具喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你幫忙把禮物送來，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天跟我<delay8 />交換禮物！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我準備的禮物，<delay8 />你還滿意嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有點擔心那禮物
會不會太孩子氣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你昨天準備的禮物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以在平安夜交換禮物，<delay8 />
感覺就像十分要好的朋友<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
昨天辛苦你了！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不僅幫忙聖誕老人送禮物，<delay8 />
還進行了交換禮物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是很厲害呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天收到聖誕老人和<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />準備的禮物，
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺就像做了一場美夢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天發生的事不是夢，<delay20 />
是真的對吧！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平安夜過得還開心嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在享用美食時，
不小心吃過頭了，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以正在反省呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
昨天是平安夜，
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有吃蛋糕嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是平安夜，<delay20 />還是聖誕節當天，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都可以吃聖誕蛋糕呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
